{"word":"πέκω","slug":"πέκω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πέκω</b></el> <el>(πέκω,) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to comb</i> or <i>card</i> wool, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>: <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <el>χαίτας πεξαμένη</el> <i>when she combed her</i> hair, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to shear</i> sheep, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b>: <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <el>πόκως πέξασθαι</el> <i>to have their</i> wool shorn, <b><a href='S:Simonides Lyricus'>Simon.</a></b> <a href='S:apud (quoted in)'>ap.</a> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}